data.description: Welcome to 2654 W 3900 S, Roy, Utah 84067! This charming home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Boasting 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, it's ideal for small families or first time home buyers!  The well-designed interior features include a fireplace, fresh paint, new carpet, and an updated kitchen.  With a spacious backyard, there's plenty of space for outdoor activities or relaxation and includes two sheds for storage and a swim spa.  This home is a gem in a sought-after neighborhood, providing a wonderful opportunity for a new chapter. Don't miss out-schedule a viewing today!   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
